{"tid":267853,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"學英文只信(near) native speakers","createTime":"2017-06-02T14:49:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T17:06:24.000Z","uid":77716,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c6ceba05bdf1798dd37302e37bb6373df61009b","tid":267853,"uid":77716,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T14:49:38.000Z","msg":"(Near) native呢兩個字冇正式的定義，為了容易討論，我就如此定義:<br />\n<br />\nNative speakers: 真正鬼佬鬼婆，一直讀國際學校，父母其中一方是native speaker，由細在外國大<br />\n<br />\nNear native speakers: 讀左幾年國際學校，外國讀書一段長時間，由細請native speaker練開英文<br />\n<br />\n土生土長香港老師根本係冇用，學生被迫每日聽港式口音，古怪造作/過度書面的用字和句構<br />\n<br />\n一定有人會鬧我話老師仲要教做人道理同考試技巧。。算鳩數啦！<br />\n<br />\n另外有人可能話native speakers的written English都未必好，事實係本地老師更多用字古怪，文法錯誤<br />\n<br />\n唔止英文科既&hellip;教中文同通識都係呃飯食居多，後者更甚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db66f13c17e999d3da000b92a2c9887d57c571da","tid":267853,"uid":41742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T14:53:24.000Z","msg":"中肯<br />\nd細路細細個就被d低質幼稚園/小學miss教壞晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bbee3778e0cec1520094c0ef25c1481702c758a","tid":267853,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T15:11:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8dfeabd87718022211d3b235a70d4f50b9c53011","tid":267853,"uid":77716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T15:27:40.000Z","msg":"有料有心的老師難得！<br />\n<br />\n冇料冇心就最多！<br />\n<br />\n冇料有心就最恐怖！"},{"pid":"3bdd2f9dd92289d4732a5f7caea575f66227bb8c","tid":267853,"uid":73404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T15:31:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有料有心的老師難得！<br />\n<br />\n冇料冇心就最多！<br />\n<br />\n冇料有心就最恐怖！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓主講既論點我有少少唔認同 但係巴打你呢句就真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n讀中學果陣高中幾年都係native speaker教英文 聽人講佢a level成績好到可以入gbus<br />\n<br />\n但佢真係完撚全唔識教書 完全咩都學唔到 我都係靠自己"},{"pid":"011c0b315268b5a793ec866da522e6f70c23bb93","tid":267853,"uid":77716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T15:50:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有料有心的老師難得！<br />\n<br />\n冇料冇心就最多！<br />\n<br />\n冇料有心就最恐怖！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓主講既論點我有少少唔認同 但係巴打你呢句就真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n讀中學果陣高中幾年都係native speaker教英文 聽人講佢a level成績好到可以入gbus<br />\n<br />\n但佢真係完撚全唔識教書 完全咩都學唔到 我都係靠自己</blockquote><br />\n你有native speaker教好幸福！就算他教學能力差，你都應該被動地學識了正確的發音和如何簡潔地表達自己意見！"},{"pid":"d2515759c7c492d9bd969ded8a190ab1fdeb0d26","tid":267853,"uid":92831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T19:24:44.000Z","msg":"本地學校學英文跟本唔關學校事"},{"pid":"1b73859c4183b492415d54e14800aa65d1b48e29","tid":267853,"uid":92831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T19:25:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本地學校學英文跟本唔關學校事</blockquote><br />\n*本地學生"},{"pid":"461d7e09d4a241ba1d5b7a8c3ae9d718c7b3dbf4","tid":267853,"uid":77716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T01:00:02.000Z","msg":"有一個老師負評了"},{"pid":"c42eb1b7a6734d174dda8dfa752f601747a5440b","tid":267853,"uid":77716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T09:46:53.000Z","msg":"強帖留名"},{"pid":"8261943e6f2838b2220b892a165f98654d04f396","tid":267853,"uid":120388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T17:06:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}